Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:48.54,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}As the memories fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.88,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}The lives of those who weren’t saved
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:59.13,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Regret and torment has come to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:03.89,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Hopelessly leading us astray
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:11.56,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}On a journey to find some kind of reason
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:16.48,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}The army’s weight is only crumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:21.03,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Haunted by the look of those who we’ve left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:26.24,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Close your eyes, try to leave the shame behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:31.54,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Who will stay to lend a helping hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:36.67,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}When death is knocking at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:42.01,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Who will fight alone for what is right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:46.68,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}For the ones who were left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:49.64,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,1,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Those who were left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:48.54,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}當記憶漸漸模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.88,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}那些未被挽救的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:59.13,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}後悔與折磨長留心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:03.89,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}使我們絕望迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:11.56,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}在尋找理由的旅途之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:16.48,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}當隊伍開始分崩離析
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:21.03,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}被拋棄之人的面龐揮之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:26.24,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}閉上眼睛想忘記愧疚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:31.54,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}誰會留下伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:36.67,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}當死亡已經近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:42.01,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}誰會獨自戰鬥追尋正義
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:46.68,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}為那些被拋棄的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:49.64,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}那些被拋棄的人們
